item.title: End of 2020
item.description: Goals for 2022 Posting how-to guides on mansoor.cf everyday Learning and growing in CyberSecurity making mansoorbarri.com a IT company Getting a job It started off really well at the beginning of this year, but as I got busier, it became a weekly thing, then monthly, and finally a seasonal thing where I would post 5 guides every 2-3 months. However, in the last quarter, I really expanded this into a polished product, which I did not expect at all.
